This is the SocialCaution Africa Edition — a privacy and digital safety platform
for African users. Built with React 18, TypeScript, Vite, Tailwind CSS.

Standing rules
- No emoji anywhere in any file
- No AI claims about any tool
- No protect, secure, ensure safety language — use check, review, assess
- No outcome guarantees — assessment framing only
- Import motion from srclibmotion — never directly from framer-motion
- Icons from lucide-react only
- Do not touch srcdataafrica — data layer is final
- Do not mix phases from BLUEPRINT.md in a single session
- FTC compliance every claim must be substantiable